org.apache.river.test.spec.lookupservice

Class QATestUtils.SrvcAttrTuple

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.river.test.spec.lookupservice.QATestUtils.SrvcAttrTuple
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Enclosing class:
    QATestUtils

    public static class QATestUtils.SrvcAttrTuple
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Class which models an event "tuple" (service,attribute,transition). This class is used by some of the tests that wish to verify that the events received from the lookup service are the events expected; based on the templates used to register event notification requests.
    See Also:
